        {
            "title": "中國｜何立峰明率團赴法國與美方舉行經貿磋商",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜何立峰明率團赴法國與美方舉行經貿磋商\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"何立峰\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:何立峰;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/何立峰\">何立峰</a>明率團赴法國與美方舉行經貿磋商</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國商務部新聞發言人周五表示，經中美雙方商定，中共中央政治局委員、國務院副總理何立峰將於3月14日至17日率團赴法國與美方舉行經貿磋商。雙方將以兩國元首釜山會晤及歷次通話重要共識為引領，就彼此關心的經貿問題開展磋商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國財政部周四表示，財政部長貝桑(Scott Bessent)將於15日至16日，在法國會見何立峰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝桑在社交媒體發文稱，他將再次與何立峰在法國巴黎會面，繼續美中貿易和經濟對話。有傳媒報道稱，美國貿易代表格里爾亦將參加有關會議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特朗普早前透露將於3月底訪華，在北京與中國國家主席習近平會面。中美雙方正在為習近平與特朗普的峰會做準備。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E4%BD%95%E7%AB%8B%E5%B3%B0%E6%98%8E%E7%8E%87%E5%9C%98%E8%B5%B4%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BF%E7%A3%8B%E5%95%86-082453041.html",
